issue comments are served (IMO correctly) with {{roleLevel}} or {{groupLevel}}.
However when posting comment while transitioning issue, {{role}} or {{group}} is expected.

For the sake of consistency we should use {{roleLevel}} and {{groupLevel}} attributes there too.

